{"article_id":"U7Rslx4vyOzlaDr6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Those shocks will continue to reverberate next week and beyond","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"because the issues involved are fundamental to American democracy ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"challenging the credibility of the White House and the vital legal institutions","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that sustain government .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"As always in politics , timing is everything ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"and the timing here raises questions about the use and possible abuse of presidential power :","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Why did Trump do it ?","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"And more importantly , why now ?","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Orchestrating the chaos , as always , was Trump himself ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"who largely stayed out of public view last week","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but managed to incite pandemonium nonetheless .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"In a dizzying sequence of events , sacked acting Attorney General Sally Yates warned in Senate testimony Monday","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that ex-national security adviser Michael Flynn was a ripe blackmail target for Russia while in office .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The President suddenly fired FBI Director James Comey on Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and then blindsided his own vice president with his shifting reasoning","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"before sabotaging the White House press operation","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that was trying to defend him .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Amid reports","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"he demanded a loyalty pledge from Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"critics warned","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Trump was guilty of a grotesque abuse of power , or even worse .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"But the President was not done .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"He suggested","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that Comey 's investigation into links between his presidential campaign and Russia were indeed the reason","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"he was fired .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"In a Friday morning tweetstorm , he seemed to suggest","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"he had a Nixon-style White House taping operation ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"and told Comey to stay mum .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Next , he proposed ending press briefings","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"because it 's impossible for his communications team to keep up with the whiplash of his stream-of-consciousness presidency .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Trump 's behavior provoked confusion and criticism in Washington .","depth":3},{"id":31,"text":"But the President is defiant","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"and may have had his detractors in mind","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"as he delivered a commencement address Saturday at Liberty University , in Virginia .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"`` No one has ever achieved anything significant","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"without a chorus of critics","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"standing on the sideline","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"saying why it ca n't be done , ''","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"`` Nothing is easier or more pathetic","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"than being a critic . ''","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"Man shoves money at lawmaker during town hall","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Man shoves money at lawmaker during town hall","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"00:44","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Meanwhile , out in the country , the political contagion is spreading .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"In North Dakota , tempers boiled over at a town hall event","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"hosted by Rep. Kevin Cramer .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"A man demanded to know","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"whether the rich would benefit from the repeal of Obamacare","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"and was escorted out by police","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"after trying to shove a wad of cash into Cramer 's collar .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"Republican Rep. Tim Walberg of Michigan was shouted down by constituents","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"shouting","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"`` health care for all . ''","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"GOP Rep. Tom MacArthur ,","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"who helped pass the Obamacare repeal bill ,","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"walked into a metaphorical bear pit in his New Jersey district .","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"`` Open your eyes ! ''","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"screamed one anti-Trump voter .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"In West Virginia , a reporter was arrested","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"after firing a string of questions at Health and Human Services Secretary Tom Price .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"At times , in Washington and elsewhere , it seemed as thought the country 's political equilibrium was at grave risk .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"It 's now normal to observe","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that Trump is not like a conventional politician ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that the point of his political project is to flout norms","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"and shake up the cozy establishment","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"and that the press takes him too literally .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"when Trump behaves in a way","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that has the media and Washington establishment types running around with their hair on fire ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"his loyal base of voters","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"who sent him to the White House","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"see a mission accomplished .","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"What do Trump 's denials on 'tapes ' and 'loyalty ' really mean ?","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"What do Trump 's denials on 'tapes ' and 'loyalty ' really mean ?","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"05:48","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"There 's also no sign","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"that congressional leaders are ready to desert him .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan , for instance , said Friday :","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"`` I 've decided","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"I 'm not going to comment on the tweets of the day or the hour . ''","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Trump went back to his seemingly impervious well of political support Friday , in a fundraising drive","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"emailed to supporters","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"in which he said :","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"`` Let 's show the hypocrites , liars , and 'elites ' of Washington","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that the American people are dead serious about our mission","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"to DRAIN THE SWAMP . ''","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"But","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"despite the loyalty of his base and for all the cacophony of the last three months , and the riotous campaign in 2016 ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"the last week has seemed different .","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"It felt at times that the White House was spinning off its political axis ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that the President was isolated even from his own staff","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"and that there was little rhyme or reason behind his increasingly erratic statements .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Trump 's often frazzled but loyal press secretary Sean Spicer was even asked in his daily briefing on Friday","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"whether Trump was `` out of control . ''","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Yet , so extreme have been the events of the last few days","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that such a question","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"-- which many would view as outrageous in more normal times --","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"did n't seem out of bounds .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Trump admits","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Russia probe was on his mind","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"when he fired Comey","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Trump admits","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Russia probe was on his mind","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"when he fired Comey","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"03:55","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"While Trump has taken America on a wild ride","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"since taking office ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"things did appear to get substantially more surreal and serious this week ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"with the possibility even looming","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that the President had edged closer to legal jeopardy with his stunning decision","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"to can Comey","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"while he was overseeing the Russia probe .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Spicer 's stand-in , Sarah Huckabee Sanders , meanwhile , made a series of statements about Comey 's popularity within the bureau and the scope of the FBI investigation","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"that were comprehensively refuted by acting FBI chief Andrew McCabe in congressional testimony on Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Some Republicans are worried about the trajectory of Trump 's presidency amid concern","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"that a distracted White House could squander its opportunity","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"to use a GOP majority","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"to reshape the country 's politics .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"`` This is ridiculous ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"it is not tenable","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"and Republicans ...","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"just politically , this can not last ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"so go ahead","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"and start holding the President accountable ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"the bogeyman is not going to come out from under your bed , ''","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Amanda Carpenter , a former communications aide to Sen. Ted Cruz said on `` Anderson Cooper 360 '' on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"`` Donald Trump 's special police are not going to come get you in the middle of the night . ''","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"`` If you say ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"'Mr . President , please respect the three branches of government .","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Please respect the American institution","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"as it 's supposed to work ' ...","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"you will be much better off , ''","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"said Carpenter , a CNN commentator .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"But beyond the politics , there 's another element to the Trump presidency","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"that makes it so discombobulating for many people .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"Thanks to the President 's mastery of social media ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"it 's hard to escape him .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"He sometimes seems to be lurking on every device , from your iPhone to your laptop to your television ,","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"and thus barges into countless conversations or social occasion .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"If nothing else , by the end of his presidency , America may face the political equivalent post traumatic stress disorder .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"And the societal damage from Trump 's perpetual war on institutions like the intelligence agencies , the courts and the media might take may years to assess .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"In that sense , Friday 's tweet storm","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"blasting Comey and the `` fake media ''","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"was just the capstone of a madcap week .","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"Timothy Naftali , a CNN historian and former director of the Nixon Library , suggested","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"that the President would do well to reconsider his approach .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"`` I believe","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"the President of the United States needs to think about his credibility , ''","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"Naftali told CNN 's Kate Bolduan ,","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"referring to Trump 's response to the investigation into alleged Russian election meddling .","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"Though there was no evidence","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"he was guilty of anything ,","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"Trump is acting like he is ,","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"Naftali said .","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"`` This is bigger than him ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"he is our head of state ,","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"he is our bald eagle ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"he represents our country .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"Perhaps there might be a time for a little bit of a moment and little reflection ...","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"perhaps he might want to think about his conduct more seriously","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"than he has up to now , ''","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":173,"text":"Spicer 's deputy holds down the fort","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":175,"text":"MUST WATCH Spicer 's deputy holds down the fort","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"01:04","depth":6},{"id":177,"text":"But it is not just Trump whose credibility seemed tarnished after his week .","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"The reputation of his press shop has also taken a hit .","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"The suddenness of Comey 's firing took the White House communications team by surprise ,","depth":10},{"id":180,"text":"but they quickly built a rationale","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"that the reason","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"Comey was gone was a damning report on his handling of the Hillary Clinton email probe","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"complied by the new deputy attorney general Rod Rosenstein .","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"It did n't seem remotely credible ,","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"but at least it was something .","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"Within hours the tale was unraveling ,","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"but not before Vice President Mike Pence had put his own reputation on the line","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"by peddling it to reporters on Capitol Hill .","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"Even though White House aides insisted repeatedly","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"the firing had nothing to do with Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"they were finally and disastrously undermined by their own boss .","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"`` In fact","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"when I decided to just do it ,","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"I said to myself ,","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"I said ,","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"'You know ,","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"this Russia thing with Trump and Russia is a made-up story ,","depth":14},{"id":198,"text":"it 's an excuse by the Democrats","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"for having lost an election","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"that they should have won , ' ''","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"Trump told NBC in an interview .","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"His comments made an already dicey job for Spicer 's team all but impossible .","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"`` I think","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"the credibility is gone ,","depth":13},{"id":205,"text":"and I 'm really sorry to say that , ''","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"said John Kirby , a former State Department and Pentagon spokesman","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"who is now a CNN analyst .","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"there is a crisis of credibility ,","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"I think","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"it is shot ,","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"and I do n't know","depth":14},{"id":213,"text":"how they ever get it back , ''","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"Kirby said .","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"Some Republicans are meanwhile worried","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"that the trust","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"that has eroded in a fraught political time for the White House","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"will leave the administration flailing","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"when an inevitable international or national crisis flares .","depth":9},{"id":220,"text":"`` Having the President undermine the credibility of his staff makes their jobs harder not just today but moving forward , ''","depth":8},{"id":221,"text":"said Republican strategist Doug Heye on CNN .","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"`` This White House has had a lot of crises but not a real true crisis yet .","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"When that crisis hits ,","depth":10},{"id":224,"text":"Sean Spicer and Sarah Huckabee Sanders , they need credibility in front of those reporters","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"who are going to be gunning after them","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"and the President hurt them today .","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"That is a real challenge for this White House . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":455,"left":268,"right":454,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":268,"left":257,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":231,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":0,"right":230,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":1,"right":229,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":234,"right":255,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":234,"left":232,"right":233,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":232,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":233,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":236,"right":254,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":8,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":254,"left":237,"right":253,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":253,"left":244,"right":252,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":240,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":13,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":14,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":241,"right":242,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":241,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":247,"right":251,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":21,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":22,"right":245,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":251,"left":249,"right":250,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":248,"right":27,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":248,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":250,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":30,"right":266,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":259,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":31,"right":258,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":258,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"context","n